Text:
WARNING!!!
Do NOT download this torrent!  It was not ripped correctly.  Apparently, one program was recording the audio while another program was playing it.  The gain was WAY too high and completely distorted (even more so than KMFDM would allow).  Also, the person who recorded it was IMing throughout.  You can hear the IM "blip" sounds in the songs.

Absolutely horrible.
holy smokes dude... Okay, I wont Download. I dont get how people can get so annoyed when its free anyway. Good lord.
